<h3><strong>Here&#39;s how you can&nbsp;try an ice water dunk at home?</strong></h3>

<p>Take a big bowl and fill it with chilled water from the refrigerator. Add some ice cubes to the bowl. Dip your face in the water for a few seconds. Repeat the process two to three times. Tap your face with a towel after taking out your makeup, and there you go.</p>

