<p><strong>Sonam Kapoor&rsquo;s haircare tips&nbsp;</strong></p>

<p>Being a hair enthusiast, Sonam Kapoor is always on the lookout for tricks and techniques that would keep her hair strong and luscious. She shared a few haircare tips from her trove of haircare wisdom:</p>

<ul>
