	<li>Be aware of your hair problems and take preventative measures at the earliest.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>A heat protectant is a must. Especially if your hair goes through constant treatments and exploitation.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Consume protein and have a balanced diet that supports hair growth and strengthening.&nbsp;</li>
